  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Pneumothorax diagnosis by an inexperienced physician in lung ultrasound</measure>
    <time_frame>May 1, 2021</time_frame>
    <description>The main endpoint will be a binary qualitative value: diagnosis of pneumothorax (yes/no) judged by inexperienced physicians performing pleural strain.</description>
